body: It's mainly because LOG(ERROR) would be a better long term solution - it also emerges in fb infrastructure better as the standard logging mechanism. I removed Warning class for now but LOG(ERROR) is dependent on glogs move, so I will convert them in an immediate followup PR once this passes.
